ster.html?user=117525><span id= >Master Solase</span></a>, <span id= > </span><br><span id=notbold>11 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Wed, Jul 31st 9:13 AM 2002</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[3.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Okay, I've been playing for sometime now, but since the macro ability has been available, I have not used it, but I'm interested in how you might have setup your macros (i.e. cast 1, pause 30, etc.. ) .&nbsp;&nbsp;Please post if you know how to create a macro that will fit in at least 3 to 4 songs in one macro (not sure if it's possible, but would really like to know).<br><br> Sol<br> 56 Bard<br> Erollisi Marr<br>&nbsp;<br>Sol<br>56 Bard<br>Erollisi Marr</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
	   <span style='font-weight: normal; font-size: 9px;'>[<a href=#top>Top</a>]</span></tr>
	   </form></table><ul>
<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=102814098015909></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f102814098015909><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=4&mid=102814098015909>RE: Macro's and Bards</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=4&mid=102814098015909#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=60483><span id=Scholar>Polyflame</span></a>, <span id=Scholar>Scholar</span><br><span id=notbold>18 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Wed, Jul 31st 2:56 PM 2002</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent<span id=notbold>[4.55]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Heres what my bard has for macros:<br><br>Slot 1:&nbsp;&nbsp;Special Attack.  Basicly this macro makes you attack, and do 3 other commands at once.  This is a good macro for just about any melee class.<br>/attack off (Stops your attack)<br>/doability 1 (That would be something like beg or sense heading)<br>/doability 2 (That would be something else like doability 1)<br>/doability 7 (That would be Instill doubt, or change it to doability 3 if you want a normal skill.)<br>/attack on (Makes you attack)<br><br>Slot 2:  General slot 1.  It's just an empty slot in your inventory with no bag or anything on it.<br><br>Slot 3:  General slot 2.  This is another inventory slot, but with an instrument like drums or strings.<br><br>Slot 4:  General slot 3.  Same as slot 2.<br><br>Slot 5:  Primary melee slot.  Its your primary weapon slot.<br><br>Slot 6:  Secondary melee slot.  Its your secondary weapon slot.<br><br>Slot 7:  Song macro.  This is pretty cool, it lets you twist a bunch of songs with the click of a button.<br>/stopsong (Stops your current song)<br>/cast 1 (Casts your first song, best if a melee song)<br>/pause 30 (Pauses for 3 seconds)<br>/stopsong (You know what it does by now)<br>/cast 2 (Plays your second song)<br><br>Slot 8:  The second song macro.  This finishes off your song macros, and lets you twist 4 at once with ease.<br>/stopsong (Duh)<br>/cast 3 (Duh again)<br>/pause 30 (I shouldnt have to do this)<br>/stopsong (Dum de dum...)<br>/cast 4 (Voila!)<br><br>Slot 9:  Whatever you want, preferably the Forage skill.<br><br>Slot 10:  Whatever you want again.<br><br>Aaaaand there you have it my musical friends, macros for a bard.  You can replace slot 9 or 10 with another instrument slot if you wish.<br><br>Hope this helps, good luckest to thou =).<br>&nbsp;<br>~Sloree<br>Nameless server<br>Level 46 Human Monk</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
	   <span style='font-weight: normal; font-size: 9px;'>[<a href=#top>Top</a>]</span></tr>
	   </form></table><ul>
<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=102830074432615></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f102830074432615><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=4&mid=102830074432615>RE: Macro's and Bards</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=4&mid=102830074432615#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=117525><span id= >Master Solase</span></a>, <span id= > </span><br><span id=notbold>11 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Fri, Aug 2nd 11:19 AM 2002</td>
