	   <tr><td colspan=2>Thanks Sloree,<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;Definately good advise, but it's what I feared though.  We can not setup one macro to play 3 songs, ugh.. But I guess setting up 2 macros to play 4 songs total isn't too bad.  And yes, I'm going to use some of this information to help me restructure my bard song lineup.  For others reading this that might have some other ideas, maybe a way to setup 3 or more songs in one macro, please let us know =) .<br>&nbsp;<br>Sol<br>56 Bard<br>Erollisi Marr</td></tr>
