<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=10280241016445></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f10280241016445><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=4&mid=10280241016445>RE: Equipping instruments</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=4&mid=10280241016445#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=173421><span id= >Quasare</span></a>, <span id= > </span><br><span id=notbold>14 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Tue, Jul 30th 6:28 AM 2002</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[3.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Hello :)<br><br>First, get three open inventory slots (With no bags on those slots). <br>Have your weapons equipped, and put two instruments in the empty inventory slots. <br>Leave one of the slots empty. Now, go to a free hotkey page. An easy way to do this is by pressing shift+2 (or+3,+4), which will take you to the second page. Move your mouse pointer to the &quot;Melee 1&quot; slot in your inventory screen. <br>Click and hold over the slot until the button pops up and is on your cursor. <br>Drag the cursor over to the first hotkey slot in the bottom left of your screen. <br>Position the cursor so the top left of the button is in the middle of the hotkey slot, <br>and click your mouse once to set that slot to Melee 1. Repeat this process for Melee 2, <br>the two instrument inventory slots, and the empty inventory slot. <br>You will now be able to switch easily between weapons and instruments, without going to the Persona screen.<br><br>Hope this help :)<br><br>Melee 1 &amp; 2 : Primary &amp; secondary slot ;)<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Wed Jul 31 06:12:10 2002</em><br>&nbsp;<br>Valaba Noirac<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=150528" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=150528</a></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
	   <span style='font-weight: normal; font-size: 9px;'>[<a href=#top>Top</a>]</span></tr>
